data.description: Discover Your Dream Home in this Picturesque Haven!Nestled in the heart of the charming Stallion Springs community, this single-family gem is the epitome of serenity and modern comfort. With 1507 square feet of living space, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a sprawling 0.28-acre lot, your new lifestyle awaits.Wood vinyl floors throughout the home lend a warm and inviting ambiance, while beautiful countertops in the kitchen provide both beauty and functionality. Plenty of space to park your boat or RV.Picture yourself preparing culinary masterpieces in this well-appointed space designed to inspire your inner chef.This newer-built home boasts contemporary appeal with open-concept living. The spacious backyard is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. Experience the true essence of California living as you savor the breathtaking sunsets in your own backyard.Here, life slows down, and quality takes center stage. Your new home is a canvas where you can paint your dreams, create lasting memories, and escape the hustle and bustle of city life.Live the Life You Deserve! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this charming, mountain home your own. Call your favorite REALTOR® today and schedule a viewing. Experience the magic of Stallion Springs - your new beginning awaits!
